<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>甜甜互动 — 哥哥的小话</title>
<style>
  body{font-family:system-ui,Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:100vh;margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffe8f0,#fff);}
  .card{width:92%;max-width:480px;background:white;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.12);padding:18px}
  h1{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px;color:#333}
  p{color:#555;line-height:1.5}
  .options{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
  button{padding:12px;border-radius:10px;border:0;background:#ff8fb5;color:white;font-weight:600}
  .small{font-size:13px;color:#999;margin-top:8px}
</style>
